{
  "$schema": "https://example.invalid/schemas/pbr_values.schema.json",
  "version": 1,
  "notes": [
    "All values are floats in the range [0.0, 1.0].",
    "These values are intended as deterministic defaults for generating packed *_pbr.png maps:",
    "  R = roughness, G = metallic, B = 0, A = 1.",
    "Per-pixel metallic is not inferred; use overrides to mark entire textures/material families as metallic.",
    "Roughness values for: brick, concrete, glass, water, ice, snow, charcoal, office paper, and base metals were aligned to the PhysicallyBased.info materials database (materials.json).",
    "Materials not present in that database remain heuristics and may need art-direction tuning.",
    "Adjust to taste after visual QA."
  ],
  "defaults": {
    "roughness": 0.85,
    "metallic": 0.0
  },
  "materials": {
    "default_block": { "roughness": 0.85, "metallic": 0.0 },
